<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF706ACFFF7D9CBD1DC2B061" pageId="139" pageNumber="899" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF706ACFFF7D9CBD1DC2B061" blockId="139.[128,1336,1803,3017]" pageId="139" pageNumber="899">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF706ACFFF7D9CBD1FE6B037" bold="true" box="[129,486,2788,2821]" pageId="139" pageNumber="899">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. The Least Woolly Bat is restricted to primary forests and most common in undisturbed areas, which suggestsit is most threatened by deforestation.
